SUMMARY:Deep Dives: An Olio House Party
DESCRIPTION:Tickets:This is a member celebration!&nbsp\; To attend this par
 ty you can sign up for our monthly membership which gives you 2 free event
 s each month. &nbsp\;You will then be able to invite one friend to the par
 ty &lt\;3&nbsp\;We're hosting a party built around obsessions\, deep dives
 \, and amateur passions.What are you obsessed with? What have you gone rea
 lly deep into — from childhood or adult life — that you don't get paid
  for?We'll spend the night giving a stage to our niche obsessions and cele
 brate each other for keeping curiosity alive! New friends\, miscellaneous 
 learnings\, deep convos and daaaaaaancing the night away.&nbsp\;What to ex
 pect:7:30pm: Come straight to the roof and upon arrival we will match you 
 with a group of friends based on our secret witchery8pm: You sit with your
  new friends and discuss a couple of curated prompts related to deep dives
  and obsessions.9pm: We'll enjoy 5\, 5-minute deep dives presented by Olio
  members. 10-11pm: DJ @usefulstyles begins and we dance our asses offTake 
 dance breaks to check out the tri-folds and little demonstrations around t
 he room to see what obsessions your friends have dove into.Enjoy a classic
  cereal bar to fuel your energy throughout the night1:30-2:30am: DJ Zimmy 
 Dynamite winds down the evening with an ambient set. We'll stretch\, and h
 ave tea because we love our bodiesTickets:This is a member celebration! To
  attend this party you can sign up for our monthly membership which gives 
 you 2 free events each month. &nbsp\;You will then be able to invite one f
 riend to the party &lt\;3&nbsp\;What is Think Olio?Think Olio is an ongoin
 g experiment in lifelong learning. We are a community of open-minded peopl
 e who gather to exchange ideas with new friends and connect over art\, lit
 erature\, and philosophy.An Olio is what we call the social learning event
 s we’ve been organizing since 2015. A blend between a lecture and a hous
 e party\, Olios are led by a teacher who loves sharing their passions and 
 the room is filled with curious\, open-minded New Yorkers.&nbsp\;Eight mon
 ths into creating a venue\, one of our favorite feelings has been the mome
 nts where we’ve stepped outside of time. We’ve created a space where c
 onversations don’t feel rushed\, people are greeted with hugs\, and as a
  community\, we spontaneously come up with new ideas (like the dial-up-dis
 co house party) and bring them to life.Our goal is to spark new perspectiv
 es\, ignite curiosity\, and enjoy ourselves socially—an alternative to t
 ypical nightlife options.Check out our full calendarDisclaimer: By purchas
 ing a ticket\, you agree to have your photo/video used for social media/ma
 rketing materials. If you prefer to not have your photo taken\, feel free 
 to send us a note.\n\nTickets & info: https://www.viewcy.com/event/deep_di
 ves_an_olio_h
URL:https://www.viewcy.com/event/deep_dives_an_olio_h
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
