SUMMARY:Lighthouse Cinema: Uncle Yanco
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Lighthouse Cinema night! Popcorn included in your t
 icket ♡Agnès Varda made Uncle Yanco in 1967 — a short\, sun-drenched 
 dispatch from San Francisco\, where she'd gone to make a documentary and i
 nstead stumbled upon a long-lost relative (?) living as a bohemian painter
  on a houseboat. The film is a delight: loose\, curious\, and shot through
  with the particular joy of discovering that eccentricity runs in the fami
 ly.At just 18 minutes\, it's Varda at her most playful and personal — a 
 proto-essay film that prefigures everything she'd spend the next five deca
 des perfecting.&nbsp\;Hang out afterwards to pour a drink and talk about w
 hat we just watched together with curated conversation prompts.- Doors ope
 n at 8:30pm - Film kicks off at 9:00pm - Chill and enjoy conversation prom
 pts exploring family roots across divides\, celebration of counterculture 
 lifestyles\, and modern-day pirates until 10:30pm.We're collaborating with
  our friends at No One's Ark for this one. Check em out!&nbsp\;Ahoy Keeper
 s of the Light! 🕯️We are the Pirates for the Planet! aboard No One’
 s Ark\, a brooklyn based non-profit thats embarked on a voyage to ressurec
 t a half sunken ship into a floating community hub for environmental youth
  education\, art\, and ecological innovation to help clean up Newtown Cree
 k\, the most polluted body of water in New York City.&nbsp\;Using purpose-
 driven piracy\, we’re raising awareness\, driving advocacy\, and providi
 ng direct action to help in the restoration of a waterway the world forgot
 . Our Ark is a vessel of change. A storytelling vehicle charting a new cou
 rse in bioremediation. A floating classroom\, laboratory\, and cultural ce
 nter. A beacon of ecological hope for the federal Superfund site we call h
 ome.&nbsp\;We've been searching for a lighthouse\, and we’re so glad to 
 have Think Olio has a beacon for us pirates! Thank you for casting your li
 ght! We love’d to have you on board…or may ye walk the plank! 🌊⚓
 ️☘️\n\nTickets & info: https://www.viewcy.com/event/lighthouse_cinem
 a_ag_1
URL:https://www.viewcy.com/event/lighthouse_cinema_ag_1
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:94c958c5-1255-4dd5-baea-918024427918@viewcy.olio
DTSTAMP:20260617T160710Z
